Committee (<span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC</span>) 旗下有八間大學（<span style=\"color: blue;\">八大</span>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XvYe59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXvYe59&h=1f0468e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VNvPLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVNvPLw&h=63a58961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中本身<ins>一成立就已經係大學嘅大學</ins>只有 <span style=\"color: blue;\">HKUST 香港科技大學</span>，其餘七大院校論獲得／有「大學」頭銜嘅歷史倒時序如下：<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1881 年：<ins>官立師範學堂 Government Normal School</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1939 年：<ins>羅富國師範學院 Northcote Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/EvNTGR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEvNTGR&h=40e17823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>葛量洪師範學院 Grantham Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ezdGkn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FezdGkn&h=c5fc7c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1960 年：<ins>柏立基師範學院 Sir Robert Black Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RCcEyv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRCcEyv&h=12ccbd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1967 年：三所師範學院易名為<ins>教育學院 Colleges of Education</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1974 年：<ins>香港工商師範學院 Hong Kong Technical Teachers' College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VqcZuB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVqcZuB&h=c0f18adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1982 年：<ins>語文教育學院 Institute of Language in Education</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FqDDTv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFqDDTv&h=dc1fc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1994 年：五所師訓學院合併為 <strong><ins>HKIEd 香港教育學院 (The Hong Kong Institute of Education)</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/nMVUzd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnMVUzd&h=8b7ef130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EdUHK 香港教育大學 (The Education University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/vCdavY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvCdavY&h=ee4a3fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1888 年：<ins>格致書院</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1903 年：<ins>嶺南學堂</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1912 年：<ins>嶺南學校</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- <strong><ins>1927-1952 年</ins></strong>：<strong><ins>嶺南大學</ins></strong>（廣州）<br />\n- 1967 年：<ins>嶺南書院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/zgSkFR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzgSkFR&h=cf3d2753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 1978 年：<ins>嶺南學院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jeNgV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjeNgV4&h=2ebe6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1999 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LU 嶺南大學 (Lingnan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jyxiWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjyxiWg&h=10cb3cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1937 年：<ins>香港官立高級工業學院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XzYfmH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXzYfmH&h=15df4cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1947 年：<ins>香港工業專門學院 Hong Kong Technical College (HKTC)</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/mbJhbW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmbJhbW&h=3831d4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/muYqzQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmuYqzQ&h=495bba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：<ins>香港理工學院 Hong Kong Polytechnic</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/MwMofP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMwMofP&h=3e6ef969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/Z9za5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ9za5V&h=c7ce1665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PolyU 香港理工大學 (The Hong Kong Polytechnic University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/fKwYmk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfKwYmk&h=6262f338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1984 年：香港第二所理工學院<ins>「香港城市理工學院」City Polytechnic of Hong Kong</ins> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/AxmUQ3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAxmUQ3&h=51b439fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CityU 香港城市大學 (City University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/TbByx8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTbByx8&h=08d3556c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 2015 年：起用新校徽 logo<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/APKnhz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FAPKnhz&h=f3da7696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>香港浸會書院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/gbktgn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fgbktgn&h=f50296c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：改稱<ins>香港浸會學院 Hong Kong Baptist College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ACbAJ4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FACbAJ4&h=6dfbd898&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/F9QYvP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF9QYvP&h=929132e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKBU 香港浸會大學 (Hong Kong Baptist University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/aFkVTK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FaFkVTK&h=c02dba86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1991 年</span></span>：<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKUST 香港科技大學 (The Hong Kong University of Science and Technology)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/LEAwFT\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLEAwFT&h=887bebfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1949 年：<ins>新亞書院 New Asia College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/WxZn5K\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FWxZn5K&h=4f2e374a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>崇基學院 Chung Chi College</ins>（由民國大陸時期十三間基督教大學遷到香港組成）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ZKUm8U\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZKUm8U&h=8da962d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1956 年：<ins>聯合書院 United College of Hong Kong</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/bcNSdS\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FbcNSdS&h=b1f2aa0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1963 年</span></span>：三院合併，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">CUHK 香港中文大學 (The Chinese University of Hong Kong)</span></span> 成立<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/p3ptNx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fp3ptNx&h=7855c725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1887 年：<ins>香港華人西醫書院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/x1igvm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fx1igvm&h=003a9f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1906 年：<ins>香港工學院</ins><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1912 年</span></span>：增設<ins>文學院</ins>，三院組成 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKU 香港大學 (The University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FnJEnJ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFnJEnJ&h=b38ba950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/024034_2a2c2a11a46bf8a94e36562bebc9dbb8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F024034_2a2c2a11a46bf8a94e36562bebc9dbb8.png&h=968107c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBlock 咗你好耐，Sor。"},{"pid":"8b7857388a00feac018c1f97710806ee4f5bf546","tid":811280,"uid":173002,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:30:52.000Z","msg":"城大開獸醫後，UGC班頭同班尾既差距越拉越遠，城大開新學科既意志值得欣賞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上面家宴既洗版post，詎係恥笑緊香港教育學院。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n官立師範學堂只係1881年開到1883年，維持兩年就停辦，只有21個師生，兩個學生畢業。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkier.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/journal/?page_id=6659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkier.fed.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fjournal%2F%3Fpage_id%3D6659&d=Jc4IlmKCiiesZzbR%2BcEhudtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bd9bdca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkier.fed.cuhk.edu.hk/journal/?page_id=6659</a><br />\n<br />\n官立師範學堂搞左兩年就早於1883年殺校，人事等各方面都無延續性，只係某學校唔滿足只追溯到1939年既歷史，將自己歷史扯埋早50年既已關閉既學校。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港第一間全日制培訓教師既院校係1916年香港大學既教師培訓部門 Department of Education (for teacher training)，為香港既學校培訓學位教師，即今日既港大教育學院。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://100.edu.hku.hk/our-history/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F100.edu.hku.hk%2Four-history%2F&d=Jc4IlmKCiiesZzbR%2BcEhudtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=aace079a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://100.edu.hku.hk/our-history/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大學教育學院並無將官立師範學堂當作自己既溯源。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日扭曲歷史宣傳香港教育大學比香港大學歷史悠久，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教大係官網連一間教會學校係1853年既課程都當作係自己歷史。某學校宣傳係香港歷史最悠久既大專院校，連自己既起源都歪曲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9afa61dd7afd0361ea68dd397093ff4494d6bc5","tid":811280,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T20:36:02.000Z","msg":"i恒能先係囉好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc3d47ac4f28c37c2500cb04ad89da8d0f93b9d","tid":811280,"uid":167443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T00:34:57.000Z","msg":"世界輪流轉"},{"pid":"9a8f7b104cabf8de84dd80768176c53b5db1aaa1","tid":811280,"uid":23495,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"視野放大啲啦，仲香港鬥香港<br />\n放眼世界既大學啦"},{"pid":"1b9eeb094c915c8879cbfa14772a009a72209e93","tid":811280,"uid":138707,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"吾城萬歲 CU ＞ ChinU 遲下做埋 香港一大"},{"pid":"bea98f73eb790cf07472d6178d3ad88532d4fb20","tid":811280,"uid":5006,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"9a8f7b104cabf8de84dd80768176c53b5db1aaa1","tid":811280,"uid":23495,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"視野放大啲啦，仲香港鬥香港<br />\n放眼世界既大學啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:18:51.000Z","msg":"呢位人兄就講得有道理<br />\n香港咁細 有咁多間當獨一面既大學好難得<br />\n但自己鬥自己始終都係純粹開心下<br />\n無咩意思<br />\n<br />\n城大起本土印象好難迫近三大<br />\n但國際研究同埋影響可以追<br />\n希望佢獸醫可以成為地區權威<br />\n增加香港影響力同國際地位之餘<br />\n仲可以突顯同大陸文化不同<br />\n而且咁樣對本土年青人未來發展都係好事"},{"pid":"85f2f2923a9dda582e60674322ce8bc90bf678a8","tid":811280,"uid":142872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dd1270cd5dd55a3d8fb84b4b0b17d9d0b00b51","tid":811280,"uid":4496,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"邊間係三大最重要都係僱主點睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShitty係老一輩心目中始終唔入流"},{"pid":"9663b6ab3a08795a52a9725fc9b3868e957be1fc","tid":811280,"uid":25971,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dadfe662bb6136e0947a6d6fab5887aa1677676a","tid":811280,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 城大個勢好似好猛，無聽見中大有咩大新聞，多數話佢排名跌，只係見到大家討論港科城學系排名，中大就潛咗水咁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:29:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">無聽見中大有咩大新聞</span><br />\nOn9 , 你冇睇新聞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家日日都有中大個乜乜副教授殺屋企人新聞囉"},{"pid":"988937f085376dbad57698d0d136db53a5a279a2","tid":811280,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}